右圖是有[[负反馈|负反馈]]電子放大器的[[方塊圖|方塊圖]]。輸入信號和一信號相減，送到[[开环增益|开环增益]]為''A''的放大器中，進行放大。放大器的輸出送到增益為''β''的反馈迴路中，再和放大器的輸入信號相減，成為放大器的輸入。环路增益可以先假設反馈迴路先在某一點切斷，再看給予一信號時的總增益。以右圖為例，环路增益是二個增益的乘積''−Aβ''，負號的原因是因為輸入信號是和反馈信號相減才送到放大器中。在放大器中，环路增益是以分貝表示的开环增益圖及閉环增益圖（1/β圖）之間的差<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://training.ti.com/system/files/docs/1332%20-%20Stability%202%20-%20slides.pdf|title = TI Precision Labs - Op-amps - Stability 2|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = |quote = To find the magnitude of AolB, we can simply subtract 1/B from Aol.|archive-date = 2016-02-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160224090134/https://training.ti.com/system/files/docs/1332%20-%20Stability%202%20-%20slides.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.analog.com/media/en/training-seminars/tutorials/MT-033.pdf|title = MT-033 TUTORIAL Voltage Feedback Op Amp Gain and Bandwidth|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = |quote = The difference between the open-loop gain and the closed-loop gain is known as the loop gain|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091123/http://www.analog.com/media/en/training-seminars/tutorials/MT-033.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.ti.com/lit/an/slyt374/slyt374.pdf|title = Operational amplifier gain stability, Part 2:DC gain-error analysis|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = |quote = ... shows the simplified open-loop gain ... along with the closed-loop gain ... The difference between these two curves is the loop gain, β×AOL.|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304062112/http://www.ti.com/lit/an/slyt374/slyt374.pdf|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

增益''A''和''β''會隨輸出信號的[[頻率|頻率]]而改變，因此环路增益也會隨頻率而變化，一般會表示為[[角頻率|角頻率]]''ω''（單位為[[弧度每秒|弧度每秒]]）的函數。

在通訊上，环路增益可以指[[载波|载波]]終端或是二線[[中继器|中继器]]上的可用[[功率|功率]]增益。最大的可用增益是由閉迴路的總損失決定，可用增益不能大於總損失。

